    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors met or exceeded required levels for MRL 2. The relative hemolysis index predictions satisfied the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all five operating points with a maximum relative error of 8.4%. Six factors were not assessed, which is acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018. The overall credibility package supports acceptance of the CFD model for the stated COU.",
